# ModuShell

ModuShell is a Python package that makes it easy to style terminal output using clean, and readable wrappers. Whether you're coloring text, applying bold or italic effects, or combining multiple styles at once, ModuShell simplifies working with ANSI escape codes ‚Äî no memorization needed.

